com.guille.ed.util.math.aks

Class Poly

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guille.ed.util.math.aks.Poly

  • public class Poly
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a polynomial class that uses BigIntegers as the coefficients It supports mod operations where the modulus is an either or another polynomial This is written for Fall 2011 CS 6150 term project
    Author:
    Vincent
